resources.string: Descarregui i instal·li funcions addicionals per a la LED View Cover. Pot crear les seves pròpies icones LED i establir-les com a icones de notificació. Per descarregar-les més tard, vagi a Ajustaments > Funcions avançades > Accessoris > LED View Cover i, a continuació, seleccioni Descarregar funcions addicionals.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
